# Ignore everything under .claude/ EXCEPT the shared project settings.json (the
# completion-gate Stop hook). settings.local.json + scratch stay ignored. Note:
# must use `.claude/*` not `.claude` — git cannot re-include a child of an
# excluded *directory*.
.claude/*
!.claude/settings.json
Claude-plans.lnk

